{"tid":2208763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[改名大法]騰訊據報於美國申請將WeChat更名為WeCom","createTime":"2020-09-19T07:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T14:07:33.000Z","uid":51271,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d8792edfd7ef7394e1e6a995d01189c65684db35","tid":2208763,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:13:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550528-20200919.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550528-20200919.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=b42bc4f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550528-20200919.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9367ebaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550528-20200919.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地科技企業騰訊，據報在美國申請將旗下WeChat微信應用程式，更改名稱為WeCom，作為WeChat的潛在替代者。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部早前宣布，將禁止涉及微信及影片分享程式TikTok的交易，牽涉多項措施，包括自本月20日起，禁止在美國境內的應用程式商店，提供TikTok及微信應用程式及更新，亦禁止微信在美國境內提供資金轉移，或處理支付的任何服務。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，根據美國專利及商標局的記錄，騰訊在上月19日，註冊了WeCom商標。報道指美國商務部長羅斯，將在當地星期日前發布監管規定，澄清哪些與微信相關的交易將被禁止。報道又引述騰訊兩位消息人士表示，WeCom不在美國對微信交易禁令的範圍內。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你改做WeCum都過唔到啦on9"},{"pid":"1df67f8570dc86d02643979043715f324e7d9043","tid":2208763,"uid":286897,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfa8b8312fdbc0e7bc4a06f96798aa8b40567db0","tid":2208763,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:16:11.000Z","msg":"弱智<br />\n禁qq旗下所有通訊app都得啦"},{"pid":"88669a80ad2e45e154b867feb78e72514839bef0","tid":2208763,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:16:37.000Z","msg":"幾時變wedead"},{"pid":"3308257de765057241d66f8fee7d48c1448629ef","tid":2208763,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"s